						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of three <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> deposited with the priests by an anonymous donor for burning three lamps during the services in the temple of Iruṅgōḷīśvaram-uḍaiya-mahādēva at Kōyāṟṟūr <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Uttamaśōḻapuram, with the ghee derived as monthly interest on the amounts.</p>						

